															</section>
							<section class="col-66 left">
																								<a class="article-title" href="/news/?id=06132016c"><h2>New App Store Review Guidelines</h2></a>
								
																<div class="article-text-wrapper">
									<p class="lighter smaller article-date">June 13, 2016</p>
																											<span class="article-text"><p>We’ve rewritten the App Review Guidelines to be more helpful, provide more context, and incorporate the guidelines for Mac apps.  We hope these updates will help your app sail through App Review. While the guidelines themselves haven’t changed, the previous App Store and Mac App Store Review Guidelines will remain available for apps currently in the review process.   <span class="nowrap"><a href="/app-store/review/guidelines/">View the new App Store Review Guidelines</a></span>.</p></span>
																																			</div>
							</section>
						</section>


					</article>
					
